{"tid":1362630,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"你哋班社團人士....","createTime":"2019-07-25T02:29:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-25T08:02:52.000Z","uid":280464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ada377a8982f356ff14adb1d7ff9f58470d393f1","tid":1362630,"uid":280464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:29:30.000Z","msg":"我係一名「和理非」的師奶。為咗今次抗爭，唔知爆咗幾多粗口。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋唔入村，唔係怕咗你；只因為我哋係普通人，知道咩叫「良知」同「人義道德」；知道咩應該做，咩唔應該做；我哋抗爭唔係為咗錢，我哋只係為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">「自由」、「公平」、「公義」</span></span></strong>而行出嚟。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">黑社會撐警，已經被人恥笑到一個點啦 ! <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong> 撐一次唔夠，仲要撐兩次，仲要玩警黑合作 !! 真心笑死人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，你哋7.21 咁做，好威咩 ? 你哋以為警黑合作，警方真係會保你哋咩? 你哋會唔會太天真呀?! 一哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />都表明同你哋割蓆啦! 而家你哋<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>一個一個被警方被何妖出賣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span>啦 ! 仲要柒出國際，真係笑爆全世界。<br />\n<br />\n你哋以為中共真係會照住你哋?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你哋又真係柒到一個點 ! 而家仲唔攪好個法治制度，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">到2047 年，你哋成條村，成個字頭都被中共滅咗都唔知咩事呀</span></span></strong> ! 乜你真係咁信中共? 白紙黑字寫到明，佢哋可以推翻，何況你哋? 中共真係會照住你哋 ? 唔好咁柒啦 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你哋都係想搵錢啫，你睇下 7.21 你哋做咗咩 ? <strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"> 好威威咁做咗場大龍鳳</span></span></strong>，結果呢?  警方照拉人，人人都唔想嚟，無晒生意，無人睇樓 ，<strong><span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">自己滅咗自己嘅地方啦</span></span></strong> ，今次真係威威啦 !<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong> 無生意、無人嚟又搵唔到錢，你哋等食屎啦 !<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">仲有呀，如果唔係香港人，你大佬「飛天哥」死撚咗啦 !</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/ERcrazydoctor/photos/a.173944479873524/419703351964301/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FERcrazydoctor%2Fphotos%2Fa.173944479873524%2F419703351964301%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=%2FPdnyacYoUlJSF57jd07D1T2VSzVBU3ss%2BeERvjOeOk%3D&h=75d3e681\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/ERcrazydoctor/photos/a.173944479873524/419703351964301/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sK19zaE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsK19zaE.jpg&h=8e514f83&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我哋係文明人，唔洗用打打殺殺、拆人伺堂嘅事去復仇嘅，只需要對準佢哋最怕嘅嘢 <strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">MEMO 紙「貼爆佢老母」</span></span></strong>，貼爆成個遊行路線，齊上齊落 ! 等佢哋篤眼篤鼻幾日都好呀 !<br />\n<br />\n發完夢啦 ! 我無嘢講。<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">齊上齊落 ! 不撤不散 ! 對準政權 ! </span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: brown;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">五大訴求:<br />\n1. 徹底撤回逃犯修訂條例<br />\n2. 撤回暴動定性<br />\n3. 釋放所有抗爭者並承諾永不追究<br />\n4. 成立獨立調查委員會調查並追究警隊濫權、濫暴、警黑合作之各事項<br />\n5. 立即實行雙普選</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d19d0b77d9a75500bfd93ab5608aafd9cbc53b4f","tid":1362630,"uid":280464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:32:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"da9119b910a5f92a8bfbd9e4997e68ae97e406b3","tid":1362630,"uid":81701,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-25T02:32:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21fe9252a2637c1f755f2fa76f733ca8ee86dd2d","tid":1362630,"uid":280464,"like":0,"dislike":0,